text: José Delfino Garcés Martínez (born 9 November 1953) is a Mexican politician from the Party of the Democratic Revolution. From 2000 to 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing the Federal District. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Mexico City Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Party of the Democratic Revolution politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
